Source.Name: paperwork
Source.Summary: Using scanners and OCR to grep paper documents the easy way
Source.Description: Paperwork is a personal document manager. It manages scanned documents and PDFs. It is designed to be easy and fast to use. The idea behind Paperwork is "scan & forget": You can just scan a new document and forget about it until the day you need it again. In other words, let the machine do most of the work for you.
